# Financial Risk Market Commodities Positions Amount

## identifier
de8041

## type
float

## definition
This is the value, as at the relevant date, in relation to positions giving rise to commodities risk (excluding gold risk), as determined in accordance with relevant prudential standards. 
 
This item includes positions (both on-balance sheet and off-balance sheet) in:
     - commodity forwards;
     - commodity futures; 
     - commodity swaps;
     - and other applicable commodity instruments (e.g. commodity options, where the entity uses a particular capital treatment approach).

For the purposes of this item and subject to prior approval from APRA, positions in foreign currency denominated commodities may be segmented into a commodity exposure and a foreign currency exposure. Only report the commodity exposure at this item.

## syntax
### xbrl
- balance=debit
- name=FinancialRisk.Market.CommoditiesPositions.Amount
- classification=baf/bafot/bafot.02.06
- period=instant
